<div style="background-color:#2A313F;color:#FFFFFF;padding:40px;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:2:57"><h1 style="text-align: center;">Kernersville Food Pantry Program</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:18px;">No one should have to choose between paying bills and putting food on the table. Our food pantry&nbsp;helps bridge the gap for families and&nbsp;individuals facing food insecurity.</span>
</p></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:3:47"></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:4:14"></div>
<div class="row my-3" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:22:92">
<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:22:92-1:2 Columns - Equal:0">
<img width="70" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/d3332bd7-1830-4d92-9d7c-497ca03083bf_download.png" alt="placeholder" class="img-fluid d-block my-3 mx-auto" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" loading="lazy" / data-zesty-id="content:images:6:26">
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:13:19"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:7:95">LOCATION</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:8:13">130 E. Mountain Street</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:9:41">Kernersville, NC 27284</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:10:10">
					Please note clients may begin lining up before&nbsp;distribution time. The car line is located beside the Kernersville Police Department.
				</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:11:38">
					<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/kYb1B7adovRFTAJ8A"><span class="btn btn-solid btn-red">DIRECTIONS</span></a>
				</p>
				</div>
<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:2columns:22:92-1:2 Columns - Equal:1">
<img width="70" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/uss-cache.salvationarmy.org/5921579e-95ce-4dbc-8db5-5e5c2c91b25c_clock.png" alt="placeholder" class="img-fluid d-block my-3 mx-auto" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;" loading="lazy" / data-zesty-id="content:images:14:56">
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:21:50"></div>
<h5 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:15:90">HOURS OF OPERATION</h5>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:16:43">Mondays, Tuesdays, and Thursdays</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:17:22">11:30 am&nbsp;- 12:15 pm</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:textarea:18:57">
					Distribution will end when supplies run out each day.
				</p>
<p style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:19:86">
